&lt;p&gt;While Airtable will be your primary platform, you‚Äôll also evaluate when other systems or tools may better serve a problem, taking a pragmatic, outcomes-first approach to how we build the People tech stack.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sitting on the People team and partnering closely with IT and internal systems, you‚Äôll use Airtable, scripting, and platform-native AI capabilities to deliver intuitive, scalable, and high-impact tools that touch every Airtable employee.&lt;/p&gt;
